ecoPrimals Watering Hole — Triple-Copyleft Licensing (scyBorg)

This repository contains three categories of content, each under its own
copyleft license. All three are governed by independent nonprofits —
no single entity can revoke them.

==========================================================================
1. SOFTWARE (Code, shaders, build scripts, configurations, tests, tools)
   License: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 or later (AGPL-3.0+)
   Full text: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html
   Governing body: Free Software Foundation (nonprofit)

   Network use triggers the distribution obligation.
   SaaS wrappers must release source.

2. GAME MECHANICS (Rules, stat blocks, progression, encounter math)
   License: Open RPG Creative License (ORC)
   Full text: https://azoralaw.com/orclicense/
   Governing body: Open RPG Creative Foundation (nonprofit)

   Irrevocable and perpetual.

3. CREATIVE CONTENT & DOCUMENTATION (Art, narrative, docs, guides, specs)
   License: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
   Full text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/
   Governing body: Creative Commons (nonprofit)

   Attribution required. Derivatives must use the same license.

==========================================================================

RESERVED MATERIAL (per ORC and scyBorg Exception Protocol):
- ecoPrimals project name and branding
- Individual primal names (BearDog, Songbird, NestGate, etc.)
- Gate names and deployment-specific configuration

